# ЁЯй╕ Real-Hero / LifeFlow тАФ Full Project Description

## ЁЯМР Project Overview

**Real-Hero** (branded as **LifeFlow**) is an **AI-First, Full-Stack Blood Donation Platform** built as a Major/Capstone project. It transforms the blood donation process from a reactive, manual system into a proactive, intelligent ecosystem driven by Machine Learning, Generative AI, real-time notifications, and gamification.

> **Core Mission:** Connect blood donors with recipients in the minimum time possible using predictive AI тАФ before a crisis even occurs.

---

