## ЁЯУж Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React.js 19, Material UI (MUI), Framer Motion, Chart.js, Leaflet, Socket.IO-Client, i18next |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js (ESM Modules), Nodemon |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas (with Geospatial indexing) |
| **Python AI Core** | FastAPI, Uvicorn, Scikit-Learn, Statsmodels, NumPy |
| **AI / LLM** | Google Gemini API (`@google/generative-ai`), Groq SDK, OpenAI SDK |
| **Auth** | JWT (jsonwebtoken), bcrypt, OTP-based email verification |
| **Email** | Nodemailer (Brevo SMTP), SendGrid (`@sendgrid/mail`) |
| **Push Notifications** | Web-Push (VAPID), Firebase Admin SDK |
| **PDF Generation** | pdfkit |
| **File Upload** | Multer |
| **Deployment** | Render (backend), Netlify (frontend) |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS + MUI + Tailwind (dev dependency) |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion, Lottie-React |
| **Internationalization** | i18next + react-i18next |
| **Maps** | Leaflet + react-leaflet |
| **OAuth** | Google OAuth 2.0 (`@react-oauth/google`), Firebase Auth |

