## ЁЯЧДя╕П MongoDB Models (11 Schemas)

| Model | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `User` | Donor profile, blood group, location, reliability score, hero points/coins, available flag |
| [Request](file:///d:/Major/backend/ai/main.py#107-111) | Blood donation request from a hospital/person тАФ blood group, urgency, geo-location, status |
| `Offer` | Donation offer from a donor in response to a Request тАФ with token-based confirmation |
| `DonorResponse` | Tracks a donor's accept/decline/delay response history |
| `Gamification` | Hero points, coins, and tier data per user |
| `Notification` | System notifications stored per user |
| `PushSubscription` | Web-Push VAPID subscription objects |
| `Offer` | Pending/confirmed donation offers with follow-up scheduling |
| `Redemption` | Record of reward redemption transactions |
| `RedemptionOption` | Configurable reward catalog items |
| `RewardLog` | Full log of point/coin earning events |
| `ChatSession` | MediBot conversation history per user |

