## ЁЯза AI & ML System

### Python AI Core (`/backend/ai/`)

A dedicated **FastAPI microservice** running on port 8000 with **8 ML endpoints**:

| Endpoint | Algorithm | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `POST /predict-acceptance` | Logistic Regression | Predicts probability a donor will accept a request |
| `POST /forecast-demand` | Holt-Winters (Exponential Smoothing) | 7-day blood demand forecast |
| `GET /forecast-all-cities` | Holt-Winters | City-wide demand forecast |
| `POST /optimize-notifications` | Q-Learning (RL) | Optimal donor notification batch size |
| `POST /train-rl-agent` | Q-Learning feedback | Online RL training loop |
| `POST /detect-fraud` | Isolation Forest | Anomaly / fraud detection |
| `POST /segment-donors` | K-Means Clustering | Donor segmentation by RFR score |
| `POST /predict-risk` | Random Forest Classifier | Blood shortage risk prediction |
| `POST /recommend-incentives` | Collaborative Filtering | Personalized reward recommendations |
| `POST /update-reliability` | Adaptive Regression | Dynamic donor trust score update |

### Analytics Dashboard ML Models (Node.js Layer)

8 models power the Analytics page, with **Node.js fallback heuristics** if the Python service is unreachable:

| Model | Visualization | Algorithm |
|---|---|---|
| **Model 1** тАФ Donor Readiness Score | Gauge Chart (0тАУ100) | Weighted Multi-Factor Scoring |
| **Model 2** тАФ Blood Shortage Risk | Risk Progress Bars | Random Forest (Python) + Heuristic fallback |
| **Model 3** тАФ 7-Day Demand Simulation | Live Bar Chart | Holt-Winters (Python) + Moving Average fallback |
| **Model 4** тАФ Donor Loyalty Tier (RFR) | Loyalty Badge (New Hero тЖТ Legendary) | K-Means (Python) + RFR heuristic |
| **Model 5** тАФ Peak Timing Predictor | Best Time Cards | Day-of-Week frequency distribution |
| **Model 6** тАФ 12-Month Impact Trajectory | Line Chart Projection | Linear Regression |
| **Model 7** тАФ Generative Insight Briefing | Text Summary Box | Rule-based NLP synthesis |
| **Model 8** тАФ Health & Recovery Advisor | Recovery Protocol UI | Biometric Stage Classifier |

---

## ЁЯФС Authentication & Security

- **Registration Flow:** Email тЖТ OTP (Nodemailer/Brevo) тЖТ Account Activation
- **Login:** JWT (stored in HTTP-only cookies) + Google OAuth 2.0
- **Password Reset:** OTP-based reset flow (`Forgot.js`)
- **Token Auth:** `authMiddleware.mjs` verifies JWT on protected routes
- **Fraud Detection:** Isolation Forest model flags suspicious users
- **Certificate Validation:** `certificateValidator.mjs` тАФ OCR + pattern matching for donor health certificates
- **CORS:** Multi-origin policy from `.env` (`FRONTEND_ORIGINS`)

---

## ЁЯУз Notification System

### Email Notifications (`emailNotifier.mjs` + `emailTemplates.mjs`)
- OTP verification emails
- Donation request alerts to matching donors
- Reminder follow-ups for pending offers (runs every **5 minutes** via `setInterval`)
- HTML-styled, branded email templates

### Web Push Notifications (`pushNotificationController.mjs`)
- VAPID-key-based Web Push API
- Service Worker support for background alerts
- Firebase Admin SDK integration

### Smart Notification Logic (`notifyController.mjs`)
- Geo-spatial query finds donors within configurable radius
- Donor sorted by reliability score and AI acceptance probability
- Token-based offer confirmation links (`/api/notify/offer/respond?token=...&resp=yes`)

---

## ЁЯОо Gamification System

- **Hero Points** earned for each donation, pledge, and milestone
- **Hero Coins** тАФ redeemable in-store currency
- **Loyalty Tiers:** ЁЯМ▒ New Hero тЖТ ЁЯж╕ Active Hero тЖТ ЁЯПЖ Champion тЖТ ЁЯСС Legendary
- **Leaderboard** for community competition
- **Rewards Catalog** (`Rewards.js`) with redemption flow

---

## ЁЯдЦ MediBot AI Assistant

- Powered by **Google Gemini API** + **Groq SDK** fallback
- Multilingual 24/7 medical chatbot
- Covers blood donation eligibility, post-donation care, FAQs
- Full chat history persistence via `ChatSession` model
- Supports markdown rendering (`react-markdown`)

---

## ЁЯФД Scheduled Background Jobs (`scheduler.mjs`)

- Periodic automated actions (e.g., proactive shortage alerts, donation drive triggers)
- Offer follow-up reminder processor runs every **5 minutes**
- Polls analytics endpoint every **60 seconds** for live dashboard updates

---

## ЁЯМН Internationalization

- **i18next** with browser language detection
- JSON locale files per language (managed by `update_locales_dashboard.py` and `update_locales_gamification.py`)
- Language switcher UI in `LanguageSettings.js`

---

## ЁЯЧ║я╕П Geo-Spatial Features

- MongoDB geospatial indexes on `User` and `Request` collections
- `$near` / `$geoWithin` queries to find donors within radius
- Leaflet map (`MapComponent.js`) showing live donor/request pins
- Distance-based sorting in the notification engine

---

## ЁЯУЬ PDF Certificate Generation

- `certificateGenerator.mjs` uses **pdfkit** to create personalized donation appreciation certificates
- Includes digital signature image, donor details, impact stats
- Downloadable from the `Profile.js` page

---

## ЁЯЪА Deployment

| Component | Platform | Config |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Netlify | `netlify.toml` тАФ SPA redirect rules |
| **Backend (Node.js)** | Render | `render.yaml` тАФ Singapore region, free plan |
| **Python AI Core** | (Local / Separate service) | Uvicorn on port 8000 |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas | Cloud cluster, URI in `.env` |

### Key Environment Variables
- `MONGO_URI` тАФ MongoDB Atlas connection string
- `JWT_SECRET` тАФ JWT signing secret
- `SMTP_HOST/PORT/USER/PASS` тАФ Brevo SMTP credentials
- `GOOGLE_GEMINI_API_KEY` тАФ Gemini LLM access
- `VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY` / `VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY` тАФ Web Push keys
- `FRONTEND_ORIGINS` тАФ Comma-separated allowed origins for CORS

